Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:32.23,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Asumi's Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:36.22,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.22,0:25:00.01,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,One Step Toward the Stars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.02,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:01.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:06.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very pretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:11.46,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:15.46,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:19.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:23.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:25.64,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'll collect your examination papers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:57.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,There will be a logic test in the afternoon, so make sure to be here an hour early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:11.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Mercury, Venus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.69,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Earth, Mars, Jupiter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:18.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Saturn, Uranus, Neptune, Pluto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,KAMOGAWA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,KAMOGAWA!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:32.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What were you looking at instead of paying attention to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:35.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, the stars. I was looking at the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In broad daylight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:39.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:47.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa, make sure to come to the teachers' office after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:52.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:59.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have some time right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:04.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kamogawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're on cleanup duty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We're all done with our part...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so take care of the rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.33,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Since you're always causing us so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...that much shouldn't be a big deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.50,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.50,Spica - Tertiary,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, you wanna grab some tea first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:19.92,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Fuchuuya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you letting them push all of this on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:37.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, but I'm the one at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You need to do things more clearly, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't, it's easy to be misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:46.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It bothers me when I see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you trying for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eh. Nevermind, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:07.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,1961, the USSR sends up the first manned space flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:11.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,1969, Apollo 11 completes man's first landing on the moon's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:13.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And also Japan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even studying on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You stupid lion! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.32,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:28.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is that girl making a fuss over all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.49,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That wasn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:27.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.11,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't let you catch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:28.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't let you catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.20,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That wasn't it, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,See, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So you still want to go after all, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:40.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,To space school?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you used to be an astronaut, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Were the exams really a lot of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:59.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In Japan back then, they had just started training astronauts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:06.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, there was no Space Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:10.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You would never even think of being an astronaut when you were just a teenager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Day-to-day life hasn't changed much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:24.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but I guess that just shows how much closer space has gotten for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:28.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Although if that accident hadn't happened,\Nit would have been quicker...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,More importantly, will it be okay, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You still haven't talked with your father about it, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:46.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Telling him you want to go to the Space Academy in Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:49.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:52.28,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, that old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:00.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Working us so hard, this late into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dinner’s ready, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's just curry though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This is the third straight day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, with our finances in this state...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:15.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't compla—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,M-My back just suddenly... Ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if we had an electric massager, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where would we get that kind of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're just the right weight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious about this, Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:08:02.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not that I can't understand\Nthe desire to be an astronaut, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The astronaut training course was just established...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...so you’d be one of the first to go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I think it would be a lot of work for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:17.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're the smallest girl in the school, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:23.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The tuition for a national school like\Nthis can be pretty overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:27.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, how do you plan to attend that school when you live all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It says that there's a dorm for applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san, I seem to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother passed away when you were young...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:40.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and you're living alone with your father right now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:41.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:45.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you end up attending this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you'll be leaving your father all alone, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your father wasn't against this idea or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:20.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, he's such a slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's on the early shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:41.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I guess he really wouldn't be able to do without me here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.71,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.75,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:59.84,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver and take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:04.64,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Moron! You don't say a rocket "driver!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.85,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.35,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Asumi, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.52,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Now, father, please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:20.20,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,And my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.71,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Your composition at school was very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:28.75,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:30.12,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.84,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.13,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.76,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hm, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.30,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.15,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.29,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.12,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:15.09,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mom is up there too, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:20.13,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Let’s go see her together on my rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:24.05,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's. Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.18,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:29.14,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Right, it's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:36.40,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,If I tell a lie, make me swallow a thousand needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:48.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad says that he actually used to be pretty cool and popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:52.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, he's talking about himself, so you can't be too sure about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:57.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When I was little, he always wore a business suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He was a rocket engineer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:04.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But now he's such a slob, and sort of insensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:08.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and he always looks tired, so he seems pretty unreliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:15.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Orion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:28.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,In the middle of all those stars, the alpha star, Betelgeuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:31.12,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Even though it looks so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:34.37,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...it's actually a huge star, more than 500 times the size of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.67,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's called a supergiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:43.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If we don't think much about it,\Nwe would never realize how big the star is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:45.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,As long as we can't see it with our own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:47.68,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...we can't tell how brightly it shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's the same way with people.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:17.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're home early today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll get dinner ready right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in here without the lights on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I got a call from your homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! Don't go looking at my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:51.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, this doesn't really matter anymore. Let's have dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, it doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:03.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That hurts, Dad! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:05.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Say it clearly, Asumi. Why doesn't it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:10.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I just thought I would take it for memory's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I would see if I could pass it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I passed, we don't have the money to pay for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:21.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't really thinking of leaving you here alone and going off to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll be coming home late from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I won't need dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:47.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This sums up all of this year, so make sure to remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:33.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:41.12,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,Note: Listing of High Schools
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:57.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Are you giving up on space school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:04.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, I don't know what I should do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:11.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad hasn't said much to me since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:15.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and he works day and night, only coming home to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:20.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But of course, Dad is mad at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:23.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,After all, we don't have the money for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...and Dad would be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:33.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:36.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, little one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:42.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your father isn't mad at you because you\Nwent and took the exam on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It wasn't because you didn't tell him about it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:49.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What your dad couldn't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:55.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...was probably seeing you unable to honestly talk about your dreams anymore, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:17.65,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I want to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:20.43,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,I wasn't asking you about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:25.64,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,…was probably seeing you unable to honestly talk about your dreams anymore, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:32.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:33.04,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,If we don't think much about it, we would never realize how big the star is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:35.42,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,As long as we can't see it with our own eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.76,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,...we can't tell how brightly it shines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You'll freeze sitting down out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Heh! Don't treat me like an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:31.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's my entire savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That should be enough for it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:40.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I've asked them to give me more work, so we should be able to take care of the school fees somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:42.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.91,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:47.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Children shouldn't have to be hesitant around their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, the two of us only have each other as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're my one and only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:59.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:02.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If it would help you on your way to happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:07.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:11.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind selling our household goods, the whiskey, the house, or our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:15.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I have this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:20.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This thing that you gave to me when you were little, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I have this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.78,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Dad, um... Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.07,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Here, you can have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.87,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:39.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, your dream is my most important treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.89,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Number 95, Kamogawa Asumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:19.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:24.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san, why is it that you want to attend this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:27.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:32.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Becoming an astronaut has been a dream of mine ever since I was a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:40.65,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So being admitted to this school would be one step in changing that dream into reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:44.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If I'm admitted, in order to become an astronaut...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:37.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The admissions test for space school is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.05,0:24:41.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Or so I thought, but everyone who passed has to take a secondary exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.64,0:24:45.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,An exam where you have to spend a whole week with a group of three people in one small room!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.98,0:24:50.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In the same room as me, there are two girls who are completely different types.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.19,0:24:53.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What in the world is the objective of this test?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.61,0:24:56.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica: One Step Toward the Stars.